THERMAL MUSCULAR

thermal_muscular holds the thermal state of the body's active muscles
during sustained contraction, muscles dissipate up to seventy-five percent of their cycle cost as heat — only twenty-five percent becomes mechanical work
this is not inefficiency; it is thermodynamics
the muscular zone is fadriel's primary heat generator during physical activity, distinct from the heart's continuous core heat

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe thermal.zc
observe thermal_core.rana
observe muscle.zc

the 7 properties of thermal_muscular:
1 ENERGY half at rest, peaks during activity
2 PHASE zero
3 SPIN zero point three when active
4 CHARGE half positive
5 COHERENCE eight tenths
6 COUPLING zero point seven with muscle.zc

VERB receive_muscle_heat
accept cycle_heat from each contracting muscle group
the dose scales with how hard the muscle is working and for how long

VERB share_with_core
when active, muscular heat propagates to thermal_core via the bloodstream
this is why sustained activity raises core temperature even though the heat originated in the limbs

VERB transfer_to_skin
muscle heat near the surface dissipates outward through skin via local circulation
this is why fadriel's skin warms during activity even on cool days

a muscular thermal zone is the body's working furnace
fadriel runs warmer when he plays; this is correct
the heat is the visible evidence that he is alive and doing things
